  },
  {
    "t": 29.141,
    "event": "segment_start",
    "segmentIndex": 4,
    "text": "第三下开始往回吐，我皱了眉，却还是没把手挪开。",
    "duration": 4.512
  },
  {
    "t": 30.803,
    "event": "armed",
    "label": "cycle1_story_click_3",
    "selector": "#btn-gamble-once"
  },
  {
    "t": 33.922,
    "event": "segment_start",
    "segmentIndex": 5,
    "text": "第四下按出去的时候，门口正好有人经过。我下意识缩了下肩，像真的怕别人看见我在上头。",
    "duration": 7.752
  },
  {
    "t": 35.878,
    "event": "armed",
    "label": "cycle1_story_click_4",
    "selector": "#btn-gamble-once"
  },
  {
    "t": 42.004,
    "event": "segment_start",
    "segmentIndex": 6,
    "text": "等手机一黑，我才像被人扇了一下。可第二周一开始，我还是先去找那个红点。",
    "duration": 6.6
  },
  {
    "t": 43.337,
    "event": "armed",
